data.description: Spacious ranch home with a great layout and tons of garage space! Make this 2 bedroom yours! From the foyer, you can look into the open living and dining room, then go on to the very nice kitchen with sliders to the deck and fenced-in back yard. The master suite in this home is sure to WOW you with a large bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a huge four-piece master bathroom, including a Jacuzzi tub. The basement is all framed up and ready to be finished, and is also stubbed for a third bathroom. This home has an attached over-sized two car garage, AND a detached 16x25 heated garage, perfect for your hobbies.
